
public class Scropion {

}

/*SCORPION

[FP] - X
[BP] - Y
[FK] - A
[BK] - B

U = Up/Jump (прыжок)
D = Down/Crouch (пригнуться/присесть)
F = Forward/Toward
B = Back/Away   


(LB/L1) = (TG) = Tag
(RB/R1) / (FP) + (FK) = (TH) = Throw (назад)
F + (RB/R1) / F + (FP) + (FK) = (TH) = Throw (вперед)
F + (FP) + (FK) = Throw Reversal
(LT/L2) / (FK) + (BK) = (FS) = Изменить стойку
(RT/R2) = (BL) = Block

Базовые приемы

 Uppercut            - Down + [BP]
 Down Slice         - Back + [BP] (hold)
 Blade Overhead      - Forward + [BP]
 Heel Kick          - Back + [FK]
 Shin Blast         - Forward + [FK]
 Sweep               - Back + [BK]


Fast Tag

 Underworld        - [BP], [FP] + [BP], Tag
 Soulless        - Back + [BP], Tag


Tag Комбо

 Eternal Vengeance    - [FP], [FP], Tag
 Punishment            - [BP], [FP], Tag
 Affliction            - Forward + [BP], [FP], Tag
 Revenge            - [FK], [FK], Tag


Комбо

 Torment              - [FP] ([FK])
 Damnation            - [FP], [FP], [BK]
 Brimstone            - [BP], [FP], [BP]
 Grave Digger         - [BP], [FP] + [BP]
 Doom Blade           - Forward + [BP], [FP], [BK]
 Dead End             - [FK], [FK], [BK]
 Grievance            - Forward + [BK], [FK]


Специальные приемы

 Spear              - Back, Back, [FP]
 Demon Fire         - Down, Back, [BP]
 Teleport           - Down, Back, [FK]
 Takedown           - Down, Back, [BK]
 Air Throw          - Block (можно выполнить и в воздухе)


Усиленные специальные приемы

 Flame Spear         - Back, Back, [FP] + Block
 Hell Fire           - Down, Back, [BP] + Block
 Flameport           - Down, Back, [FK] + Block
 Takeout             - Down, Back, [BK] + Block


X-Ray Move

 Scorpion Sting     - Flip Stance + Block


Финишные приемы (фаталити)

 Split Decision     - Forward, Down, Forward, [BP]
 Nether-Gate           - Back, Forward, Back, [FK] (Sweep)
 Stage fatality     - Forward, Up, Up, [FP]
 Babality              - Down, Back, Forward, Down, [BP]
 Klassic Fatality     - Down, Up, Up, [BP] (с расстояния прыжка)

*/